<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CS:CO Na stiahnutie | Lukasss895</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-red: #ff0000;
            --dark-bg: #0d0d0d;
            --card-bg: #1a1a1a;
            --text-gray: #b0b0b0;
        }

        body { 
            background: var(--dark-bg); 
            color: white; 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center; 
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Hlavný kontajner, ktorý vycentruje kartu */
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* Akčný a moderný dizajn karty */
        .csco-download-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-red);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .csco-download-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        /* Dekoratívne červené svetlo na pozadí karty */
        .csco-download-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50px;
            right: -50px;
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background: var(--primary-red);
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        /* Tvoj panáčik, ak ho máš (ak nie, nevadí) */
        .mini-panacik {
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5));
        }

        /* Nadpisy */
        h1 { 
            color: white; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        h2.subtitle {
            color: var(--primary-red);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* Popis hry */
        .game-desc { 
            line-height: 1.8; 
            color: var(--text-gray); 
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px auto;
        }

        /* Veľké, herné tlačidlo na stiahnutie */
        .download-btn { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: var(--primary-red); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 22px 50px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 50px; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            transition: 0.3s; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            box-shadow: 0 5px 25px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .download-btn:hover { 
            background: transparent;
            border-color: var(--primary-red);
            color: var(--primary-red);
            transform: scale(1.05); 
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.7); 
        }

        /* Spätný link pod kartou */
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 50px;
            color: #555;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="csco-download-card">
            
            <img src="lukas-oprava.png" alt="Lukáš" class="mini-panacik">
            
            <h1>CS:CO (Classic Offensive)</h1>
            <h2 class="subtitle">Návrat Legendy</h2>
            
            <p class="game-desc">
                Priprav sa na čistý Source engine zážitok v temnom, hernom dízajne. 
                Vysoko výkonná optimalizácia, ikonické zbrane bez skinov, staré modely a pohyb, ktorý si zamiluješ. 
                Pripomeň si staré dobré časy CS 1.6!
            </p>

            <a href="https://gofile.io/d/TUJyr3" target="_blank" class="download-btn">
                📥 STIAHNUŤ HRU (ZIP)
            </a>

        </div>

        <a href="index.html" class="back-link">← Späť na domovskú stránku</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
